= Introduction =

This wiki page compares the security-focused, hardened defaults of {{project_name_short}} against upstream [https://www.debian.org Debian]. The differences are comprehensively detailed in several tables and visually highlighted below. The aspects considered are security hardening, several privacy aspects, and usability aspects.

